metadata.name: Pop Fizz Paleta Pals #1
metadata.description: The coldest NFT's on the market.  A collection of 4444 unique NFT's with built in utility from day 1!  First off, all NFT's will act as a loyalty card that gives you free paletas and it is the first half of a licensing agreement that allows you to open your own Pop Fizz mobile ice cream truck.  NFT holders of this collection will be added to the whitelist for our second NFT drop in late 2022 which, when combined with an OG Pop Fizz Paleta Pal nft, provides full licensing for a franchise.   1 NFT in this set will win you your own fully functioning Pop Fizz Paleta Truck and all equipment to start your own Pop Fizz once you take title of the truck.  Join our discord for more details!: https://discord.gg/nMychnuweC  Twitter: @PaletaPalNFT
